        <abstract> 
<p>Finds from the Colonial Office that a census [of the Pitcairn Islands?] is expected soon, from which he will get the information he desires. [See <hi rend="doubleUnderline">9241</hi> and <hi rend="doubleUnderline">9246</hi>.]</p> 
